							Use of select commands
							-----------------------

PROGRAM
-------

names='Adam Ben Carl Dom'
PS3='Select names: '
select name in $names
do
    if [ $name == dom ]
      then
        break
    fi
    echo "hello $name"
done

OUTPUT
------

1) Adam
2) Ben
3) Carl
4) Dom
Select names: 1
hello Adam
Select names: 2
hello Ben
Select names: 3
hello Carl
Select names: 4
